fields.description:
This is working:

Ti.Contacts.createPerson({
           firstName : 'First',
           lastName : 'Last',
           address : {
               'work' : [workAddress1]
           },
           phone : {
               work : [workPhone],
           },
});


This is not:

Ti.Contacts.createPerson({
           kind: Ti.Contacts.CONTACTS_KIND_ORGANIZATION,
           organization: "Company",
           address : {
               'work' : [workAddress1]
           },
           phone : {
               work : [location.phone],
           },
});

It creates an empty contact in the iOS addressbook.
